review_data.title: Sweet treats
review_data.content: Beautiful little cafe just outside of Zurich. Worth checking out the area if you're close by at the wild life park. You'll welcome the more reasonable prices compare to Zurich city. Chocolates were delicious as expected and the bircher was beautiful.
